    "In the process of molecular representation, the typical approach involves information extraction and correlation based on the atom level.",
    "However, SPE enhances widely used atom-level encodings by appending human-readable and chemically interpretable SMILES substrings as encodings for SMILES pairs (Fig. 2).",
